headline: IBM faces suit over Weather Channel site users’ data, Bloomberg says
summary: IBM (IBM), which owns The Weather Channel website, is facing a proposed class action alleging the company violated federal privacy law by sharing personal information of users who watched videos online to advertisers without consent, Bloomberg’s Cassandre Coyer reports, citing the suit.
